Amawaṭ n umaklas imezdi yettili-d [[azuk|wazuk-is]] gar n 220 ar 460 g (azal afellay deg 150 ar 500 g), Teɣzi n [[tafekka|tfekka-s]] 20 cm ma d asallaf-is 5 cm 

